title: New: Azealia Banks – Fuck Up The Fun (Prod. By Diplo)
content:
I’m still to be convinced by Azealia Banks.

Sure, I find her music rather interesting, but not to the point of me actually wanting to relisten; it’s just an experience that gets tiresome rather quickly. New track, Fuck Up The Fun produced by none other than Diplo is supposedly a diss towards Iggy and T.I. yet as far as put downs go, it’s fairly weak. There’s plenty of Azealia’s stereotypical highly offensive spouting, however, to be honest, it’s getting monotonous; come on Azealia, we know you’re better than this. At least it has a good beat, right?
